data.description: 12325 Midway Church is looking for it's new owners! This charming 3 bedroom, 2  bath home is nestled on half acre lot. Yard has plenty of room for kids to play with a little stream right across the street. Upon entering, you will be invited by the cozy fireplace and open floorplan. LVP flooring throughout. Kitchen has butcher block countertops. This is a great opportunity for buyers who want a well-maintained home and the flexibility to upgrade over time. Contact your real estate agent today to schedule a showing and explore the potential of this lovely property.
